      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:8:1:42:5",
      "text": [
        " إِنَّ لِإِبْلِيسَ عَوْناً يُقَالُ لَهُ تَمْرِيحٌ إِذَا جَاءَ اللَّيْلُ مَلَأَ مَا بَيْنَ الْخَافِقَيْنِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "<a id=\"_Toc492473432\">H 14752</a> – From him, from Salih, from Ali Bin Al-Hakam, from Abaan Bin Usman, who has said:",
          "<span class=\"first-chapter-phrase\"><span class=\"first-in-chapter character-a\">A</span>bu Abdullah</span><sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘Iblees<sup>la</sup> has a helper called ‘تَمْرِيحٌ’ Tamreeh. When the night comes, he fills what is between the two palpitations (of the heart)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "304. From him, from Salih, from Ali Bin Al-Hakam, from Abaan Bin Usman, who has said: Abu Abdullah (a.s.) has said: ‘Iblees (la) has a helper called ‘تَمْرِيحٌ’ Tamreeh. When the night comes, he fills what is between the two palpitations (of the heart)’."
        ]
      }
